# {{lb|en|chiefly|physics}} Without physical [[tension]]; in a state of [[equilibrium]]. {{defdate|from 19th c.}}
# {{lb|en|physiology}} Of a [[muscle]]: [[soft]], not [[tensed]]. {{defdate|from 19th c.}}

